pma:database.name: biologicaldb
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `log` ( `sensorID` int(11) NOT NULL, `timestamp` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `temperature` float NOT NULL, `humidity` float NOT NULL, `voltage` float NOT NULL ) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `sensors` ( `sensorID` int(11) NOT NULL, `X` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `Y` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `current_voltage` float NOT NULL, `state_ok` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1', PRIMARY KEY (`sensorID`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;
